== 背景與製作 ==
電影從1998年8月至12月在[[巴黎|巴黎]]、[[諾昂維克_(安德爾省)|諾昂維克]]和[[威尼斯|威尼斯]]取景攝製。[[茱麗葉·畢諾許|畢諾許]]說，[[喬治·桑|喬治·桑]]最吸引自己的一點是她是個堅強有力的女子，但同時又很脆弱。<ref>{{cite news | title = Following Sand's footsteps | url = http://www.irishtimes.com/newspaper/weekend/1999/0320/99032000201.html | format = fee required | publisher = The Irish Times | date = 1999-03-20 | accessdate = 2007-09-13 | archive-date = 2012-10-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20121012154841/http://www.irishtimes.com/newspaper/weekend/1999/0320/99032000201.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>

